10 report as required in this subsection.
11
12 SECTION 12. Arkansas Code § 25-43-1303(f), concerning the duties of
13 the Secretary of the Department of Parks, Heritage, and Tourism, is repealed.
14 (f)(1) By November 1 of each odd-numbered year, the secretary shall
15 provide an oral report to the Legislative Council on the state of the
16 department.
17 (2) The Legislative Council shall schedule an appropriate date
18 and shall give notice thereof to the secretary of the date on which the
